name: The Sorrowful Lady
description:
Atop a hill, eternally gazing into the horizon, stands the Sorrowful Lady.
No one knows who she is, no one knows why she is there and no one knows the cause of her mournful cries.
Although she will acknowledge the presence of others near her, nothing has ever made her interrupt her somber ritual. Few try, anyway, for only those with hardened hearts can even tolerate the sense of loss and regret brought by the mere sight of her.
